 - Women can exchange clothes to rotate outfits and refresh their wardrobe on a regular basis. 
 - Teens can exchange prom/homecoming outfits. Men can exchange ties. (Just kidding.) 

You can swipe left for outfits you are passing on, swipe right for outfits you like. 
